He Was Found In The River | Mystery Thriller Movie | Edward Burns | Jennifer Ehle | The River King

Abel Grey investigates the death of a boy who was found in a river; fearing scandal, the school insists it was self inflicted, but Abel suspects that a dangerous schoolboy initiation went horribly wrong. 

2005.  Stars: Edward Burns, Jennifer Ehle, Thomas Gibson, John Kapelos
